text:
Ah, Hinana.
What's up? Wasn't today supposed to be a lesson?

Yeah, that's right.
But it's already over~

I see... How was the lesson?
Did you master the choreography?

Yeah~, it was fine.
I got praised by the trainer~

Is that so? That's impressive. What about
everyone else? Have they already gone home?

Hmm~ I don't know~ Koito-chan said
she'll practice a bit more before leaving though.

...I see.
Looking forward to Noctchill's stage.
